data.description: This meticulously maintained, move in ready Shea-built “Morning Glory” open concept model with gracious and welcoming covered front porch offers 2 bed/2 bath with den and additional flex/dining room. Newly painted interior throughout, including all doors and baseboard trim. The home features hard-surface tile floors throughout (no carpet), Plantation shutters on all windows throughout, including lanai door. Abundant natural light with large windows throughout. The oversized kitchen features a large island, granite countertops, 42” cabinets with new hardware, custom back splash, stainless appliances, gas stove, newer LG refrigerator, and large walk-in pantry. This model offers a unique “Smart Room” with storage galore that acts as an office/ craft room/laundry room all in one.  42” cabinets with new hardware and custom back splash in this area as well. Large master bedroom and master bath features dual vanities, granite countertops, large shower with built-in bench, private water closet, and convenient, oversized walk-in closet for storage and organization. The screened-in lanai looking out at your fully fenced and landscaped back yard is the perfect spot to enjoy a morning cup of coffee or a relaxing bug free evening outdoors. New water heater replaced in Dec. ‘22.  The home is located in beautiful/historic Deland within a gated 55+ community offering a private resort-style pool, fitness room, clubhouse with restaurant-style dining and bar, lighted tennis & pickle ball courts, bocce ball, and much more to enjoy. This is a great neighborhood for walking, biking, and staying active. There is also a championship golf course nearby. Convenient access to I-4, shopping, restaurants, beautiful downtown Deland and just a short drive to the beautiful Atlantic Ocean beaches or Orlando and attractions.
